  "description": "The Gorenje two-chamber refrigerator presented in 2020 belongs to the middle class of devices. Due to the height of 200 cm, the model will please with a good capacity: the useful volume reaches 331 liters, which should be enough for families of two to four people. The Gorenje NRK 6201 PS4 refrigerator does not require labor-intensive maintenance, including manual defrosting, since the Full No Frost system is implemented here. The 96-liter freezer has three drawers: one open and two with a transparent front wall. Here you can freeze up to 12 kg of food per day, including thanks to the quick freezing function. In addition to open shelves, the 235-liter refrigerator compartment contains a CrispZone container for vegetables, and there are also four door baskets. Other useful features include AdaptTech technology, which automatically reduces the temperature when the doors are opened frequently, the presence of touch controls with support for the EcoMode vacation mode. It is also important that the model does not create any particular acoustic discomfort (noise up to 38 dB) and is very economical (class A+). In addition to the version in silver colours, a similar unit in white can be found on the market.",
